  "detailed_description": "Embark on a unique adventure in search of the coveted sacred flour in this exciting action roguelike. Take on a world where flour and swords meet, and traverse an ever-changing dungeon filled with creatures that are both bizarre and adorable.<br><br>Armed with a wide variety of weapons and resources you'll find along the way, you'll have to fight your way through enemies and challenging bosses. Didn't get it right the first time? Don't worry, every attempt is a new opportunity, as the dungeon changes with each playthrough, offering a fresh and renewed challenge each time.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186760/extras/1b48231ea2c548bfd5b533cf555b1032.poster.avif?t=1767696736\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186760/extras/1b48231ea2c548bfd5b533cf555b1032.webm?t=1767696736\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186760/extras/1b48231ea2c548bfd5b533cf555b1032.mp4?t=1767696736\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Physics-based melee combat:</strong> Feel the weight and impact of every hit in a physics-based combat system.<br></li><li><strong>More than 50 different weapons:</strong> From crisp swords to blunt sledgehammers, adapt to the situation with the weapons you find.<br></li><li><strong>Special moves:</strong> Find unique skills and moves that will give you an edge in battle.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186760/extras/87060199efd06de36b716e4a1131b36c.poster.avif?t=1767696736\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186760/extras/87060199efd06de36b716e4a1131b36c.webm?t=1767696736\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186760/extras/87060199efd06de36b716e4a1131b36c.mp4?t=1767696736\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186760/extras/d17c879625162561f0cc5d5519e905bb.poster.avif?t=1767696736\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186760/extras/d17c879625162561f0cc5d5519e905bb.webm?t=1767696736\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186760/extras/d17c879625162561f0cc5d5519e905bb.mp4?t=1767696736\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Epic boss fights:</strong> Test your skills against powerful and memorable bosses.<br></li><li><strong>Constantly changing dungeons:</strong> No playthrough will ever be the same, each game can give rise to new challenges.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186760/extras/5e0032716955554417824a1a4332a7a4.poster.avif?t=1767696736\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186760/extras/5e0032716955554417824a1a4332a7a4.webm?t=1767696736\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186760/extras/5e0032716955554417824a1a4332a7a4.mp4?t=1767696736\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><strong>Interaction with curious characters:</strong> Discover and chat with a variety of quirky characters throughout your adventure.<br></li><li><strong>Complete Bestiary:</strong> Collect information about all the creatures, regions and weapons you encounter in your own bestiary.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186760/extras/0d9cfdc2586ed4b4c698a25ee83ddbcf.poster.avif?t=1767696736\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186760/extras/0d9cfdc2586ed4b4c698a25ee83ddbcf.webm?t=1767696736\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186760/extras/0d9cfdc2586ed4b4c698a25ee83ddbcf.mp4?t=1767696736\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186760/extras/36943a30fd3c8a11d84154778593e7ae.poster.avif?t=1767696736\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186760/extras/36943a30fd3c8a11d84154778593e7ae.webm?t=1767696736\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186760/extras/36943a30fd3c8a11d84154778593e7ae.mp4?t=1767696736\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Get ready for a gameplay experience that combines frantic action with a touch of creativity and humor. Do you have what it takes to get the sacred flour?",
